# Architecture & Security Audit

On every file change, Cursor must check:

## Security Checklist
- No reentrancy vectors (.call{value:})
- No tx.origin usage
- No unchecked external calls
- No timestamp manipulation (block.timestamp for <= comparisons)
- Proper access control on all state-changing functions
- No selfdestruct or delegatecall without audit

## Code Quality
- No mock/placeholder data in production files
- Every API call uses real backend endpoints
- Every contract call uses verified ABI + address
- No hardcoded addresses or keys
- UTF-8 encoding, no garbled Chinese characters
- Files ≤ 300 lines (split if larger)

## Reference
Full audit: run `node skills/ion-dex-commander/scripts/audit-local-code.mjs`
